<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div id="overlay" class="overlay"></div>
    <button id="toggleBtn" class="toggle-arrow">
        <span>Book Appointment</span><i></i>
    </button>
    <section id="appointmentSection">
        <%- include('partials/appointmentForm') %>
        <br><br>
    </section>

    <div class="container2">
        <div>
            <h1>BBMH Hospital â€“ Best Cardiology Hospital in Bhilwara</h1>
            <img src="\images\cardio.jpeg" alt="Cardiology at BBMH" class="img">
            <ul>
                <li><b>What is Cardiology?</b> Cardiology is a medical specialty focused on the diagnosis and treatment of heart and blood vessel disorders.</li>
                <li><b>Expert Care:</b> BBMH Hospital offers expert cardiologists with vast experience in managing both acute and chronic cardiac conditions.</li>
                <li><b>Advanced Diagnostics:</b> Equipped with modern tools like ECG, echocardiography, treadmill test (TMT), and Holter monitoring for accurate assessment.</li>
                <li><b>Treatment Services:</b> We provide medical management, angiography, angioplasty, pacemaker implantation, and heart failure care.</li>
                <li><b>Preventive Cardiology:</b> Lifestyle counseling and early risk detection for high blood pressure, diabetes, and cholesterol.</li>
                <li><b>Emergency Response:</b> 24/7 emergency care for cardiac arrest, heart attacks, and other critical cardiac events.</li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <h4 style="color: cadetblue;">Cardiac Conditions We Treat:</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Coronary Artery Disease (CAD)</li>
                <li>Heart Failure</li>
                <li>Arrhythmias (Irregular Heartbeats)</li>
                <li>Congenital Heart Defects</li>
                <li>Hypertension and Stroke Prevention</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container3">
        <div class="wrapper" style="margin-top: 8vh;">
            <img src="\images\cardio2.webp" alt="Cardiac Treatment">
            <div class="intro">
                <h2>Comprehensive Heart Care:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Diagnosis:</b> Non-invasive and minimally invasive cardiac evaluations to detect heart diseases early.</li>
                    <li><b>Treatment:</b> Personalized plans including medication, lifestyle changes, and interventional procedures.</li>
                    <li><b>Rehabilitation:</b> Post-treatment cardiac rehab for long-term recovery and improved heart function.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="wrapper1">
            <img src="\images\cardio3.jpg" alt="Angioplasty Procedure">
            <div class="intro1">
                <h2>Angioplasty and Stenting:</h2>
                <p>Angioplasty is a procedure to restore blood flow through narrowed or blocked coronary arteries. A small balloon is inflated to open the artery and may be followed by stent placement to keep it open, ensuring proper blood circulation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>
        <div class="wrapper2">
            <div class="intro2">
                <h2>When to See a Cardiologist:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Persistent chest pain or pressure</li>
                    <li>Shortness of breath or dizziness</li>
                    <li>Irregular heartbeats or palpitations</li>
                    <li>High blood pressure or cholesterol</li>
                    <li>Family history of heart disease</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div class="video-container">
        <div style="padding: 2vh;">
            <h2>Why Choose BBMH Hospital for Cardiology?</h2>
            <p>BBMH Bhilwara provides comprehensive heart care with top-tier cardiologists, advanced diagnostics, and modern intervention techniques. Our patient-first approach, 24/7 emergency cardiac support, and focus on long-term heart health make us a trusted destination for heart treatment in Rajasthan. With personalized attention and the latest medical technology, we ensure the best outcomes for every patient.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            document.getElementById("toggleBtn").addEventListener("click", function () {
                let appointmentSection = document.getElementById("appointmentSection");
                appointmentSection.style.display = (appointmentSection.style.display === "none" || appointmentSection.style.display === "") ? "block" : "none";
            });
        });

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            document.getElementById("toggleBtn").addEventListener("click", function () {
                window.scrollTo({
                    top: 10,
                    behavior: "smooth"
                });
            });
        });
    </script>

    <script>
        (() => {
            'use strict';
            const forms = document.querySelectorAll('.needs-validation');
            Array.from(forms).forEach(form => {
                form.addEventListener('submit', event => {
                    if (!form.checkValidity()) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        event.stopPropagation();
                    }
                    form.classList.add('was-validated');
                }, false);
            });
        })();
    </script>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
